“Nuclear meltdowns, that explains the bald–”
Velocity grappled toward Eudora.
Fuck!
No!
Jhansi–
–intercepted.
She grabbed Velocity’s arms.
The two Asterlings struggled against each other.
Jhansi shouted, “Open the fucking door!”
Nobody moved.
Velocity screamed in Jhansi’s face.
“Man fuck you!”
Jhansi screamed back.
“Fuck you too!”
She tried to pin Velocity’s arms back but found it impossible to overpower them.
Velocity twisted free of Jhansi’s grip and smashed her against the back of Nancy’s seat.
Nancy reached over the seat, dug her nails into the soft flesh beneath Velocity’s wrists, and pried apart the two special ones.
Velocity ground their teeth.
“Fuck you.”
They vibrated in place.
“Deadbeat princess rescued once again.”
Binyelum opened their mouth but Jhansi spoke first.
“Velocity! Everyone makes mistakes!”
Another light flared in the distance.
Velocity wrenched free from Nancy’s grip.
Hot pain exploded across Jhansi’s cheek.
Velocity had–
–slapped her?!
Jhansi blinked.
Velocity shouted, “Mistakes?!”
They squeezed both their fists.
“You think this is some kind of misunderstanding?”
They gestured wildly with open palms.
“Whoops, our beloved leader accidentally forgot to mention that one of us is not just a fascist but also a goddamn child molester.”
They gestured again.
“Whoops, the fascist accidentally forgot to save me!”
They gestured again.
“Whoops, the fascist tripped and fell and saved the bimbo that was trying to kill me!”
Velocity hammered their head with both fists.
“Boy oh boy, we sure are fucking accident prone, aren’t we?!”
