“Basically.”
Velocity barked.
“You idiot! I’m twenty-eight!”
Wait–
–what?!
Jhansi whirled around.
“What?!”
Everyone stared at her.
Jhansi’s chest tightened.
“Hang on …”
She shook her head.
“What?”
She shook her head again.
“What the fuck does that mean?”
Binyelum cocked their head.
“Jhansi–”
Jhansi jabbed a finger at Velocity and whirled to face Binyelum.
