Velocity raised their eyebrows.
“Secret faith?”
Jhansi smiled.
“Yes.”
She leaned in closer.
“I’m an ultrare specialing.”
Another light flared in the distance.
Binyelum said, “Jhansi–”
Jhansi shook her head.
“No. I want to do this.”
Velocity snorted.
“You’re a netorare specialing?”
Jhansi scoffed.
“Haha.”
She shook her head.
“I’m going to save everyone.”
Eudora laughed.
Binyelum said, “Jhansi!”
Jhansi held up a hand.
Velocity paused.
Their brows fell slowly, until they carved deep furrows in Velocity’s face.
Velocity addressed everyone.
“Oh, no.”
They frowned.
