“Man, I don’t know what to think!”
They gestured harder.
“I thought I’d found some friends for the night–”
They shook their head.
“–but really I’m just surrounded by assholes and liars and lunatics."
Sebastian said, “Surrounded by all.”
Everyone turned to him.
He gestured.
