“You know that this is your punishment.”
Sebastian beseeched the ceiling with hands curled into claws.
“Pejudo lo anmo I fucking know.”
He raked his claws through his hair.
“That’s the whole fucking point!”
He stabbed a claw at his chest.
“That’s why I’m–”
He stabbed a claw toward the earth.
“–here.”
He gestured around.
“This is my fucking punishment.”
His chest heaved.
Everyone stared at him.
Nancy blinked slowly.
Binyelum cocked their head.
“The Asterlings are your punishment?”
Tears welled in Sebastian’s eyes.
“Yes.”
His hands softened and fell to his lap.
“That’s what I asked for.”
